                <div class="block-header" style="display: none;">
                    <h2><small><b>Password Zone <em>(Attention !!)</em></b> <b>New Password</b> : <em>leave blank if you don't want to change it</em> <br><b>Current Password</b> : <em>we need your current password to confirm your changes</em></small></h2>
